H
(e_n)
\sum_n\left\langle x,e_n \right\rangle^2 = \left\|x\right\|^2 = \left\langle x,x \right\rangle
\left\langle x,y\right\rangle = \sum_n \left\langle x,e_n \right\rangle \left\langle y,e_n \right\rangle, 
\langle x, e_n \rangle = x_n
(e_n)
\langle y,e_n \rangle = y_n
 \langle x,y \rangle = \sum_{n} \langle x , e_n \rangle \langle y , e_n \rangle = \sum_{n} x_n y_n, 
(e_n)
\langle x,y\rangle=\sum x_{i}y_{i}
